<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="25Aug1937"><font color="red">25 August 1937</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Dr Von M[?]knopp saw me &hellip; He says I am better &hellip; can find nothing wrong with my organs &hellip; to account for the violent attacks of intestinal pain &hellip; It may be due, as my wife thinks, to overwork in Paris &hellip; Russia - (The storm is over) Keep till my return sending words of Soldier&apos;s Song &hellip; Where is Dr Berman&apos;s book, I ordered it from Brentano&apos;s before I left &hellip; I am very weak &hellip; I can&apos;t work again for some days at least </div>
